object.property: SELECT * FROM (SELECT ROUND((sum(pinhits)*100)/sum(pins)) "LibraryCacheHR" FROM v$$librarycache) a, (SELECT ROUND(((SUM(gets)-SUM(misses))*100)/SUM(gets)) "LatchesHR" FROM v$$latch) b, (SELECT ROUND((1-(phy.value / (cur.value + con.value)))*100) "DBCacheHR" FROM v$$sysstat cur, v$$sysstat con, v$$sysstat phy WHERE cur.name = 'db block gets' AND con.name = 'consistent gets' AND phy.name = 'physical reads') c, (SELECT ROUND(ms.VALUE/ DECODE((ds.VALUE+ms.VALUE),0,1,(ds.VALUE + ms.VALUE))*100) "SortInMemory" FROM v$$sysstat ds, v$$sysstat ms WHERE ms.NAME = 'sorts (memory)' AND ds.NAME = 'sorts (disk)') d, (SELECT DECODE(SIGN(ROUND((ec.VALUE-pc.VALUE)*100/DECODE(ec.VALUE,0,1,ec.VALUE))),-1,0, ROUND((ec.VALUE-pc.VALUE)*100/DECODE(ec.VALUE,0,1,ec.VALUE))) "ExecuteParseHR" FROM v$$sysstat ec, v$$sysstat pc WHERE ec.NAME = 'execute count' AND pc.NAME IN ('parse count', 'parse count (total)')) e;

SELECT a.current_utilization "CurrProcesses", DECODE(TRIM(a.limit_value),'UNLIMITED',TO_CHAR(a.current_utilization),a.limit_value) "MaxProcesses", b.current_utilization "CurrSessions", DECODE(TRIM(b.limit_value),'UNLIMITED',TO_CHAR(b.current_utilization),b.limit_value) "MaxSessions", c.current_utilization "CurrParServers", DECODE(TRIM(c.limit_value),'UNLIMITED',TO_CHAR(c.current_utilization),c.limit_value) "MaxParServers", d.current_utilization "CurrShaServers", DECODE(TRIM(d.limit_value),'UNLIMITED',TO_CHAR(d.current_utilization),d.limit_value) "MaxShaServers" FROM v$$resource_limit a, v$$resource_limit b, v$$resource_limit c, v$$resource_limit d WHERE a.resource_name='processes' AND b.resource_name='sessions' AND c.resource_name='parallel_max_servers' AND d.resource_name='max_shared_servers';

SELECT a.bytes "RedoBuffers", b.bytes "BufferCache", c.bytes "SharedPool", d.bytes "LargePool", e.bytes "FixedSGA", f.bytes "StreamsPool", g.bytes "FreeSGA", h.bytes "JavaPool", i.bytes "MaximumSGA", j.value "SGATarget" FROM v$$sgainfo a, v$$sgainfo b, v$$sgainfo c, v$$sgainfo d, v$$sgainfo e, v$$sgainfo f, v$$sgainfo g, v$$sgainfo h, v$$sgainfo i, v$$parameter j WHERE a.name='Redo Buffers' AND b.name='Buffer Cache Size' AND c.name='Shared Pool Size' AND d.name='Large Pool Size' AND e.name='Fixed SGA Size' AND f.name='Streams Pool Size' AND g.name='Free SGA Memory Available' AND h.name='Java Pool Size' AND i.name='Maximum SGA Size' AND j.name='sga_target';

SELECT a.value "Logons", b.value "OpenCursors", c.value "Commits", d.value "Parses", e.value "PhysicalReads", f.value "PhysicalWrites", g.value "LogicalReads", h.value "BytesSentClient", i.value "BytesReceivedClient", j.value "BytesSentDBLink", k.value "BytesReceivedDBLink", l.value "SessionCPU", m.value "Executions", n.value*TO_NUMBER(vp.value) "BytesSentGC", o.value*TO_NUMBER(vp.value) "BytesReceivedGC" FROM v$$sysstat a, v$$sysstat b, v$$sysstat c, v$$sysstat d, v$$sysstat e, v$$sysstat f, v$$sysstat g, v$$sysstat h, v$$sysstat i, v$$sysstat j, v$$sysstat k, v$$sysstat l, v$$sysstat m, v$$sysstat n, v$$sysstat o, v$$parameter vp WHERE a.name='logons cumulative' AND b.name='opened cursors cumulative' AND c.name='user commits' AND d.name='parse count (total)' AND e.name='physical reads' AND f.name='physical writes' AND g.name='session logical reads' AND h.name='bytes sent via SQL*Net to client' AND i.name='bytes received via SQL*Net from client' AND j.name='bytes sent via SQL*Net to dblink' AND k.name='bytes received via SQL*Net from dblink' AND l.name='CPU used by this session' AND m.name='execute count' AND n.name='gc current blocks received' AND o.name='gc current blocks served' AND vp.name='db_block_size';

SELECT NVL(a.time_waited,0) "WaitOther", NVL(b.time_waited,0) "WaitApp", NVL(c.time_waited,0) "WaitConf", NVL(d.time_waited,0) "WaitConc", NVL(e.time_waited,0) "WaitCommit", NVL(f.time_waited,0) "WaitNet", NVL(g.time_waited,0) "WaitUserIO", NVL(h.time_waited,0) "WaitSysIO", NVL(i.time_waited,0) "WaitAdmin", NVL(j.time_waited,0) "WaitCluster", NVL(k.time_waited,0) "WaitQueue", NVL(l.time_waited,0) "WaitSched" FROM v$$system_wait_class a, (SELECT 'Other' wc FROM dual) ax, v$$system_wait_class b, (SELECT 'Application' wc FROM dual) bx, v$$system_wait_class c, (SELECT 'Configuration' wc FROM dual) cx, v$$system_wait_class d, (SELECT 'Concurrency' wc FROM dual) dx, v$$system_wait_class e, (SELECT 'Commit' wc FROM dual) ex, v$$system_wait_class f, (SELECT 'Network' wc FROM dual) fx, v$$system_wait_class g, (SELECT 'User I/O' wc FROM dual) gx, v$$system_wait_class h, (SELECT 'System I/O' wc FROM dual) hx, v$$system_wait_class i, (SELECT 'Administrative' wc FROM dual) ix, v$$system_wait_class j, (SELECT 'Cluster' wc FROM dual) jx, v$$system_wait_class k, (SELECT 'Queue' wc FROM dual) kx, v$$system_wait_class l, (SELECT 'Scheduler' wc FROM dual) lx WHERE a.wait_class(+)=ax.wc AND b.wait_class(+)=bx.wc AND c.wait_class(+)=cx.wc AND d.wait_class(+)=dx.wc AND e.wait_class(+)=ex.wc AND f.wait_class(+)=fx.wc AND g.wait_class(+)=gx.wc AND h.wait_class(+)=hx.wc AND i.wait_class(+)=ix.wc AND j.wait_class(+)=jx.wc AND k.wait_class(+)=kx.wc AND l.wait_class(+)=lx.wc;
